name: P E P I R A

metadata.name: Daft Pepe
metadata.description:
A famous moment from the anime where a motorcycle drifts in front of a cyberpunk city. 
 A Daft Punk helmet and an angry Pepe in the background perfectly complement the atmosphere of chaos!
 Can our hero save the city from chaos and disorder? 
1/1 digital art by Max ZKH ----- 4400*5200px / JPG
